Enter a world of tragedy and despair, led by horror impresario and game master Ivan Van Norman. This captivating series, based on a game of tragic horror, includes a cast of 40 players, all DOOMED, one game master, and zero survivors. Ten Candles was designed by Stephen Dewey and published by Cavalry Games. It is available for sale at cavalrygames.com

What you are seeing is a role-playing game played with dice. This is collaborative storytelling where people take on a character, and improvise a story as that character. They will occasionally roll dice to see if they succeed or fail at certain tasks.
